accessibility.text: There is darkness and silence all around you.
It's wired. You seem lose the connection with your physical body. You can't figure out why you are here, how long you've been here, or even who you are.
The only one thing you are sure is that you've never had similar experience before. You are trying to feel something other than darkness and silence, but nothing happens.
All you can do now is either waiting or quit this strange story.
